author: liyin
msg: [master] Fix bug in TimestampsFilter that returns deleted KeyValue under certain circumstance
TimestampsFilter gives hint for matcher to make a jump over KeyValues whose timestamps
are not in request list. However, delete marker could also be ignored so that the result contains
deleted KeyValues. This change is to disable the smart jump feature. If smart jump feature is
fixed in the future, we can turn on it again.
Test Plan: Add a new unit test that reproduces this scenario
